    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been reviewed under MRL-5 requirements for a Class III VAD device. Seven factors were formally assessed and all returned achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and are flagged as epistemic gaps. The overall credibility package does not meet the required thresholds; the submission is not accepted for regulatory submission without remediation of the identified gaps. This record is filed under ProfileMinimal; a content hash is provided for integrity tracking but no digital signature has been applied to this package.",
